  "labels": [
    { "releaseType": "major", "name": "Version: Major", "overwrite": true }
  ]
}
Add none releaseType. This will act as a skip-release unless paired with a SEMVER label{
  "labels": [{ "releaseType": "none", "name": "documentation" }]
}
